OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ask 72-year-old farmer Huanchun Cao    
OL,6, about his pension and he reacts with a 
OL,7, throaty cackle.                        
OL,9,FHe sucks on his home-rolled cigarette, 
OL,10,Fnarrows his brow and tilts his head -  
OL,11,Fas if the very question is absurd. "No,
OL,12,Fno, we don't have a pension," he says  
OL,13,Flooking at his wife of more than 45    
OL,14,Fyears.                                 
OL,17,FA slowing economy, shrinking government
OL,18,Fbenefits and a decades-long one-child  
OL,19,Fpolicy have created a creeping         
OL,20,Fdemographic crisis in in Xi Jinping's  
OL,21,FChina.                                 
